COMMANDS_HELP = "<b>Command List:</b>\n\n - <b>/help</b> (or <b>/h</b> or <b>/?</b>)\n   Displays this page\n - <b>/version</b> (or <b>/ver</b> or <b>/about</b>)\n   Information about the version.\n - <b>/whoami</b>\n   Information about you.\n - <b>/whois</b> [<b>character name</b> (or <b>*account name</b>)]\n   Information about a character or an account.\n - <b>/f a</b> (or <b>/f +</b>) [<b>character name</b> (or <b>*account name</b>)]\n   Adds the character or the account to your Friend list.\n - <b>/f d</b> (or <b>/f -</b> or <b>/f r</b>) [<b>character name</b> (or <b>*account name</b>)]\n   Deletes the character or the account from your Friend list.\n - <b>/ignore a</b> (or <b>/ignore +</b>) [<b>character name</b> (or <b>*account name</b>)]\n   Adds the player or the account to your Enemy list.\n - <b>/ignore d</b> (or <b>/ignore -</b> or <b>/ignore r</b>) [<b>character name</b> (or <b>*account name</b>)]\n   Deletes the player or the account from your Enemy list.\n - <b>/w</b> (or <b>/msg</b> or <b>/whisper</b>) [<b>character name</b> (or <b>*account name</b>)] [<b>message</b>]\n   Sends a private message to a player or an account.\n - <b>/t</b> [<b>message</b>]\n   Sends the message to team members only.\n - <b>/g</b> [<b>message</b>]\n   Sends the message to guild members only.\n - <b>/p</b> [<b>message</b>]\n   Sends the message to the group members only.\n - <b>/a</b> [<b>message</b>]\n   Sends the message to players of the same alignment who are in the same area.\n - <b>/r</b> [<b>message</b>]\n   Sends a request to join a guild to players in the same area.\n - <b>/b</b> [<b>message</b>]\n   Sends an offer to buy or sell items to players in the same area.\n - <b>/m</b> [<b>message</b>]\n   Sends an offer to meet new adventurers to players in the same area.\n - <b>/away</b>\n   Activates / Deactivates the Away mode in order to receive/block private messages.\n - <b>/list</b> (or <b>/players</b>)\n   Lists the name of the characters that are fighting.\n - <b>/kick</b> [<b>character name</b>]\n   Expels a player from a fight. Can only be used before launching the fight!\n - <b>/spectator</b> (or <b>/s</b>)\n   Activates / Deactivates the spectator mode for your fight.\n - <b>/invite</b> [<b>character name</b>]\n   Invites the player to join the group.";
